    <description>
        PicoContainer is a small, simple container for arbitrary components. It is embeddable and
        extentensible.  PicoContainer is designed for server and client
        side, for small and enterprise applications. There are
        already quite a few diverse containers that deliver the PicoContainer design.
        Components can be created for it without importing or extending any
        interfaces or classes outside of the java.* package.  Components also have no
        meta-info specification. I.e. no XML. Most importantly of all, components for PicoContainer
        can be used without PicoContainer for good old-fashioned hard-coded deployments.
    </description>
